msgid ""
"[skull]: -X. X is the number of [[Glyph]] cards in the victory display."
"[cultist]: -2 (-4 instead if there is a [[Stowaway]] enemy at your location)."
"[tablet]: -2. If your location is flooded, reveal another token."
"[elder_thing]: -4. If this token is revealed during an attack or evasion attempt, take 1 damage or 1 horror."
msgstr ""
"[skull]：–X。X为胜利区中[[字符]]卡牌的数量。"
"[cultist]：–2（如果你所在地点有[[偷渡虫]]敌人，改为–4）。"
"[tablet]：–2。如果你所在地点已淹没，再揭示一个混乱标记。"
"[elder_thing]：–4。如果攻击或躲避尝试期间揭示本标记，受到1点伤害或1点恐惧。"

msgid ""
"[skull]: -X. X is 1 more than the number of [[Glyph]] cards in the victory display."
"[cultist]: -3 (-5 instead if there is a [[Stowaway]] enemy at your location)."
"[tablet]: -3. If your location is flooded, reveal another token."
"[elder_thing]: -5. If this token is revealed during an attack or evasion attempt, take 1 damage and 1 horror."
msgstr ""
"[skull]：–X。X为胜利区中[[字符]]卡牌的数量+1。"
"[cultist]：–3。（如果你所在地点有[[偷渡虫]]敌人，改为–5）"
"[tablet]：–3。如果你所在地点已淹没，再揭示一个混乱标记。"
"[elder_thing]：–5。如果攻击或躲避尝试期间揭示本标记，受到1点伤害或1点恐惧。"

msgid "The Great Lift and Sliding Locations"
msgstr "大升降机和滑动地点"

msgid "Time seems to slip away as you follow the dark tunnels out of the heart of the city. Eventually the constant churn and thrum of machinery melts away, replaced by an ominous silence. Andy has only just proposed that you turn around to find another route when the endless stairs come to a stop. An intricately carved door is set in the ceiling above you. Pressing a panel in its center reveals a vast, airy structure that vaguely resembles the nave of some ancient alien cathedral. A towering lift dominates the center, surrounded by spiraling ringed floors. The walls are covered in countless alien glyphs, pulsing with green light. You wonder if the great archive might hold anything valuable."
msgstr "你沿着黑黢黢的隧道远离城市的心脏，时间也随你一起流逝。最终不断的扰动和机械的轰鸣都消散了，取而代之的是不祥的静默。安迪刚刚建议你，在无尽楼梯的终点转过去找另一条路。你头顶就有一扇雕刻精致的门。你按下中央的面板，门外是一座巨大的建筑，悬在空中，看着像是某种远古大教堂的内殿。最中央是一架高耸的升降机，周围螺旋环绕着楼层。墙上数不尽的异星符文都闪着绿光。你好奇宏伟的档案库里会不会有什么珍贵的东西。"

msgid ""
"You land on the top floor of the towering nave. Twisting stairs and catwalks circle the sprawling structure, revealing more levels below. The walls around you are covered in glowing alien glyphs: hundreds of thousands of symbols covering every surface. You wonder if the great archive might hold anything valuable."
"“Watch yourself. We’re not the first ones here,” says Ruby. The jewel thief is bent over a prone human body lying in a pool of fresh blood. You’re struck by their colorful patchwork cloak. A deep, rumbling roar reverberates through the chamber. Ruby’s expression turns grave."
"“If we’re going to find anything of value, we’d better act quickly.”"
msgstr ""
"你踏上了巍峨的内殿之顶。扭曲的楼梯和狭窄步道围绕着肆意伸展的建筑，露出下面的更多楼层。你周围的墙上都覆盖着发光的异星文字：千百计的符号盖住了所有表面。你好奇宏伟的档案库里会不会有什么珍贵的东西。"
"“小心点，我们并非第一批来客。”露比说道。珠宝大盗弯腰看向新鲜血泊里俯躺的尸体，尸体身上的彩色补丁长袍吸引了你的注意。深沉的隆隆吼声震撼了整个厅室。露比的表情严肃了起来："
"“要是我们想找到什么有价值的东西，最好赶快行动。”"

msgid "If an investigator has the \"Plumb the Depths\" task:"
msgstr "如果调查员有“追本溯源”任务："

msgid "Task: Plumb the Depths"
msgstr "任务：追本溯源"

msgid ""
"You can’t help but marvel at the austere grandeur of the ancient structure. Was this an ancient palace? A library? A place of worship? The intricate murals on the walls are a blend of pictograph and alien writing, depicting an ancient migration across the stars. The glyphs glow with a flickering green light, chronicling unknowable histories, ancient secrets hidden from humankind."
"One image—a nightmarescape of oceanic horrors and sunken cities—catches your attention. You press the eye of a particularly disturbing creature and feel a rush of ancient memories. Thoughts and feelings of an alien being, images of the stygian depths of some distant planet, overwhelm your consciousness. The memories give way to clearer, more defined facts, dates, a history recorded by a prehistoric civilization. You begin to feel yourself slip away as though your consciousness were being drawn through a sieve. There is much more you could learn… but should you?"
msgstr ""
"你不禁赞叹起这座古代建筑的古朴宏大。这是古代的宫殿吗?还是图书馆?抑或宗教场所?墙上精妙的壁画混合了象形文字和异星文字，描绘了一场星际之间的迁徙。字符闪着幽幽绿光，记录着不为人知的历史、人类毫无了解的古代秘密。"
"有有一幅图——梦魇般的海底恐怖和沉没城市—吸引了你的注意。有只生物特别吓人，你按下它的眼睛，远古记忆随即汹涌而来。异星存在的思维和感受，遥远行星阴森深海的景象，都占据了你的意识。这些记忆转而变成了更清晰、更确定的事实、日期，还有史前文明记录的历史。你感到自我在流逝，仿佛是意识被筛子滤过。还有很多你可以探知的……但你应该这么做吗？"

msgid "<i>Look away.</i>"
msgstr "<i>看向别处。</i>"

msgid "Erase 1 progress under “Plumb the Depths” in your Campaign Log. Each investigator begins the next scenario with 1 clue <i>(from the token pool)</i>."
msgstr "在剧本日志中，“追本溯源”下擦去1进展。每位调查员带有1个线索开始下一场冒险<i>（从供应堆拿取）</i>。"

msgid "<i>Seek the truth.</i>"
msgstr "<i>探求真相。</i>"

msgid "Mark 2 progress under “Plumb the Depths” in your Campaign Log and suffer 1 mental trauma. Each investigator begins the next scenario with 1 fewer card in their opening hand."
msgstr "在剧本日志中，“追本溯源”下记录2进展并承受1点精神创伤。每位调查员少1张起始手牌开始下一场冒险。"

msgid "Put the Twisting Catwalks, West Antechamber, East Antechamber, and Ancient Altar locations into play according to the location placement diagram."
msgstr "按照地点摆放示意图所示，将扭曲窄道、西前厅、东前厅、古代祭坛放置入场。"

msgid "Shuffle each copy of Crumbling Archives and remove one of them from the game at random. Put each remaining copy of Crumbling Archives into play as shown in the location placement diagram."
msgstr "混洗每张崩塌档案馆，将其中随机一张从游戏中移除。将剩余的每张崩塌档案馆按照地点摆放示意图所示放置入场。"

msgid "Twisting Catwalks"
msgstr "扭曲窄道"

msgid "Crumbling Archives"
msgstr "崩塌档案馆"

msgid "West Antechamber"
msgstr "西前厅"

msgid "East Antechamber"
msgstr "东前厅"

msgid "Great Lift"
msgstr "大升降机"

msgid "Ancient Altar"
msgstr "古代祭坛"

msgid "Put the Great Lift location into play on level 1, <i>(Inactive)</i> side faceup. (See <b>The Great Lift and Sliding Locations</b> below)."
msgstr "将大升降机地点放置入场，位于1层，<i>（关闭）</i>面朝上。（见下方的<b>大升降机和滑动地点</b>）。"

msgid "Build the act and agenda deck using agenda 1a-\"Ruined Archives,\" agenda 2a-\"Unstable Foundations,\" act 1a-\"Steps of Giants,\" and act 2a—\"Escape the Tower (v. 1).\" Remove each other act and agenda from the game."
msgstr "使用密谋1a“毁坏的档案馆”和密谋2a“动荡的地基”创建密谋牌库；使用场景1a“巨人的阶梯”和场景2a“逃离高塔（版本一）”构建场景牌库。将其他每张场景和密谋从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Search the <i>Star Spawn</i> encounter set for the Star Spawn Observer enemy and set it aside, out of play. Remove two other cards in the <i>Star Spawn</i> encounter set from the game at random."
msgstr "查找<i>星之眷族</i>遭遇组，找出星之眷族观测者敌人，将其放在一边，位于场外。将<i>星之眷族</i>遭遇组中随机两张其他卡牌从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play at East Antechamber."
msgstr "每位调查员从东前厅开始游戏。"

msgid "Put the Great Lift location into play on level 4, <i>(Inactive)</i> side faceup. (See <b>The Great Lift and Sliding Locations</b> below)."
msgstr "将大升降机地点放置入场，位于4层，<i>（关闭）</i>面朝上。（见下方的</b>大升降机和滑动地点<b>）。"

msgid "Build the act and agenda deck using agenda 1a-\"Flooded Archives,\" agenda 2a-\"Unstable Foundations,\" act 1a—\"Steps of Giants,\" and act 2a—\"Escape the Tower (v. II).\" Remove each other act and agenda from the game."
msgstr "使用密谋1a“淹没的档案馆”和密谋2a“动荡的地基”创建密谋牌库；使用场景1a“巨人的阶梯”和场景2a“逃离高塔（版本二）”构建场景牌库。将其他每张场景和密谋从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Search the <i>Star Spawn</i> encounter set for the Star Spawn Observer enemy and set it aside, out of play. Remove each other card in the <i>Star Spawn</i> encounter set from the game."
msgstr "查找<i>星之眷族</i>遭遇组，找出星之眷族观测者敌人，将其放在一边，位于场外。将<i>星之眷族</i>遭遇组的剩余卡牌从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Each investigator begins the game on the Twisting Catwalks."
msgstr "每位调查员从扭曲窄道开始游戏。"

msgid "Increase the flood level of each location on levels 1 and 2."
msgstr "提升1层和2层的每个地点的淹没等级。"

msgid "Increase the flood level of each location on level 1 so that they are fully flooded."
msgstr "提升1层的每个地点的淹没等级，以使其完全淹没。"

msgid "Set the Shard of Y'ch'lecht story asset and the Colossal Tyrant enemy aside, out of play."
msgstr "将伊库勒刻特碎片剧情支援和巨型霸王敌人放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "Also gather <i>The Inescapable</i> encounter set. Set The Inescapable enemy aside, out of play."
msgstr "收齐<i>穷途异魔</i>遭遇组卡牌，将穷途异魔敌人放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "During this scenario, the investigators will need to use the Great Lift to explore other levels of the tower."
msgstr "本场冒险期间，调查员需要通过大升降机探索塔楼的不同楼层。"

msgid "Locations are not connected to one another except via the Great Lift, their connection icons, or certain card effects."
msgstr "除了通过大升降机及地点各自的连接图标，以及特定的卡牌效果之外，地点彼此之间都不连接。"

msgid "The Great Lift is only connected to the locations to the left and right of it, and vice versa."
msgstr "大升降机只与其左边和右边的地点相互连接，反之亦然。"

msgid "When instructed to slide the Great Lift up or down, move the Great Lift to the level above or below its current level."
msgstr "在受到指示要将大升降机向上或向下滑动时，就将大升降机从当前的楼层向上或向下移动一个楼层。"

msgid "The Great Lift cannot move above level 4 or below level 1."
msgstr "大升降机不能移动到第4层之上，也不能移动到第1层之下。"

msgid "When the Great Lift moves, each card and token at that location moves with it."
msgstr "在大升降机移动时，该地点的每张卡牌和每个标记也随之一起移动。"

msgid "Cross out \"Court of the Ancients\" on the R'lyeh map."
msgstr "在拉莱耶地图上划掉“远古宫廷”。"

msgid "Was the Shard of Y'ch'lecht under the control of an investigator when the scenario ended?"
msgstr "冒险结束时，是否有调查员控制了伊库勒刻特碎片？"

msgid "Check the box next to \"Shard of Y'ch'lecht\" under \"Artifacts Earned.\""
msgstr "在“取得的神器”部分，“伊库勒刻特碎片”旁的方框内打勾。"

msgid "Shard of Y'ch'lecht"
msgstr "伊库勒刻特碎片"

msgid "The rest of the expedition tell you they found you standing at the edge of the towering climb as if sleepwalking. You rub your eyes. You have no memory of the alien court. And, given that it has almost entirely collapsed, you never will."
msgstr "探险队的其余成员告诉你，他们发现你站在高耸的峭壁边缘，仿佛是在梦游。你擦了擦眼睛，异星的宫廷你一点儿也不记得了，而且，由于它已经完全崩塌，你也永远不会记得了。"

msgid "Steeling yourself for another climb, you put one hand above the other, moving from handhold to handhold as the tower threatens to collapse under you. Eventually you pull yourself to the lip of the shattered dome and out to safety. Andy clambers out of the ancient court, followed by the rest of the expedition. You all look down at the dazzling skyline of R’lyeh, which seems to shift and sway strangely in the strong sea winds."
msgstr "塔楼就要在你身下垮塌，你坚定地继续攀爬，在一个个能抓手的位置一下下前进。最后你终于来到了破碎穹顶的边缘，到了安全的地方。安迪和探险队的其余成员也爬出了远古王庭。你们一起低头望向拉莱耶令人目眩的天际线，它似乎正在强劲的海风中诡异地变换摇曳。"

msgid "After prodding and twisting at every ridge of the dais, it finally slides open. Below, a spiral stairway descending into deep darkness below. Another chunk of rock shatters on the floor of the ancient building. “We have to get out of here!” Ruby shouts. Wasting no time, you descend the stairs, leaving the crumbling tower and its ancient secrets behind."
msgstr "你截戳扭扭了平台的每个角落，终于让它滑开了。里面的阶梯螺旋而下，通往深不见底的黑暗。又一块巨石砸碎在古建筑的地上。“我们得离开了！”露比叫道。你没有浪费时间，冲下阶梯，把崩塌的塔楼和远古的秘密都抛在了身后。"
